Description: This comprehensive R package is designed to empower data analysis and exploration
		by providing a collection of interactive Shiny modules. This package allows users to 
        seamlessly visualize and explore their data with a wide range of visualization tools 
        including heatmaps, PCA plots, violin plots, scatter plots, box plots, survival analysis,
		methylation analysis, and more. Whether importing and filtering data, assessing coverage or examining intricate
		patterns, this package offers an intuitive and interactive interface for effortless data
		visualization and exploration.
